             <a href="https://github.com/Viren070/stremio-addon-manager" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Viren070</a>.
             Thanks also to Sleeyax &amp; &lt;Code/&gt;.
           </p>
+          <p class="muted elf-footer-cta">
+            Need managed hosting?
+            <a
+              class="elf-footer-link"
+              href="https://store.elfhosted.com/product-category/stremio-addons/?utm_source=cinebye&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=footer_cta"
+              target="_blank"
+              rel="noopener"
+            >See ElfHosted Stremio options</a>
+          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="right">
           <a class="btn-link" href="https://github.com/0xConstant1/stremio-addon-manager" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source Code</a>
@@ -62,6 +71,19 @@
 .credits a { color: #8fc7ff; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
 .credits a:hover { color: #b6dbff; }
 
+.elf-footer-cta { font-size: 0.95em; }
+.elf-footer-link {
+  color: #8fc7ff;
+  text-decoration: underline;
+  text-underline-offset: 2px;
+}
+.elf-footer-link:hover { color: #b6dbff; }
+.elf-footer-link:focus-visible {
+  outline: 2px solid #3794ff;
+  outline-offset: 2px;
+  border-radius: 2px;
+}
+
 .btn-link {
   display: inline-flex;
   align-items: center;
